lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur can already feel the benefit of their training camp in Barcelona after a gruelling period of matches in recent weeks, striker Harry Kane said.

headline.print_headline: Kane Says Spurs Feeling Benefits of Barcelona Training Camp
